                        f is it dyryuate? of what substaunce is it / &amp; wher
                        
                           ••
                        re serueth it? Answere. It is sytuate vnder the 
                           •
                        ayde muscles, and it so named of Pery / that is to 
                           ••
                        y rounde aboute, and of Tonnes / that is to say 
